含peaceful: just so you guys know that her videos don’t represent the actual living standards of chinese people living in rural areas. her home is probably the only decently organised and tidied country residence in rural areas of china. the vast majority of the people that live in rural or mountainous areas in china are poorly educated and have limited access to natural resources, let alone modern technologies. existence of conventional customs and ways of thinking that are outdated and even seem stupid can easily be found in these remote regions. dog thieves that poison and steal dogs in order to sell the meats to certain restaurants that serve dog meats are quite common in these rural areas as well. i can go on and on all day long to talk about what the actual country life in china looks like, but i want to thank her for making these peaceful videos that show the western world the beautiful side of her life as an ordinary country girl living in mainland china, and for the amazing portrait of hard working chinese people that value the idea of family, especially taking actual care of the elderly, above all.
含peaceful中文翻译: 只是让你们知道她的视频并不代表居住在农村地区的中国人的实际生活水平。她的家可能是中国农村地区唯一有组织和整洁的乡村住所。居住在中国农村或山区的绝大多数人受教育程度不佳，获得自然资源的机会有限，更不用说现代技术了。在这些偏远地区可以很容易地发现常规习俗和过时甚至看起来似乎很愚蠢的思维方式。狗盗贼毒和偷狗以将肉类出售给某些狗肉的餐馆，在这些农村地区也很普遍。我可以整天继续谈论中国的现实乡村生活，但我要感谢她制作的这些和平的视频，这些视频向西方世界展示了她作为一个普通的乡村女孩生活的美丽一面在中国大陆，以及对中国努力工作的惊人肖像，这些肖像重视家庭的想法，尤其是对老年人的实际照顾。

含peaceful: this is what school should teach us. why are we living so hard? trying to best each other. trying so hard, but for what? recognition ? appreciation? preservation ? if we all just stopped, if we all just listened, if we all were to breathe from the depths of our hearts, if we were to live.... the world wouldnโ€t be so bad. because there would be nothing we would be living for. no ideals, no trying to one up, no competition, no bloody suck ups. if money was not a thing and if we arenโ€t so selfish then we could get by. taking only the amount we need. sharing and not discriminating, not hating, not killing. then the world we live in wouldnโ€t be sinking? living as one, living peacefully, just like the animals all around us. taking only what they need and nothing more. theyโ€ve survived longer then us yet the amount of time we have existed is a chip of what they have and what have we done? killed this earth. schools should have taught us how to harvest wool, how to clean wool, how to make clothing. schools should of taught us how to cook with the life around us. schools should of taught us not to be selfish, not to want, not to become greedy like the people before us. instead we learn about multiplying aโ€s,bโ€s and cโ€s, learning about history, singing do re mi. but for what? to get a job, to earn money, to eat too much, to become corrupt, to listen to leaders who donโ€t give a fuck. this is what it means to live. like her. yet we live a life of such unhappiness. trying to buy too much trying to earn too much. when all we need is just a little. keep it simple. what have we done.
含peaceful中文翻译: 这是学校应该教我们的。我们为什么这么努力？试图互相最好的。尝试这么努力，但是什么呢？认出 ？欣赏？保存？如果我们都停下来，如果我们都倾听的话，如果我们都要从我们的内心深处呼吸，如果我们要活下去。...世界不会那么糟糕。因为我们将没有什么可以为之而来的。没有理想，没有尝试一个人，没有竞争，没有流血的吮吸。如果钱不是一件事情，如果我们不是那么自私，那么我们就可以通过。只拿我们需要的金额。分享，不歧视，不讨厌，不杀人。那么我们生活的世界不会沉没吗？像我们周围的动物一样生活，和平地生活。只采取他们需要的东西，仅此而已。他们的生存比我们更长，但是我们已经存在的时间是他们拥有的东西以及我们做了什么的筹码？杀死了这个地球。学校应该教我们如何收获羊毛，如何清洁羊毛，如何制作衣服。学校应该教我们如何与周围的生活一起做饭。学校应该教会我们不要自私，不要想要，不要像我们之前的人们那样变得贪婪。取而代之的是，我们了解了乘以A，B和C的繁殖，了解历史，唱歌Do Mi。但是什么？找工作，赚钱，吃得太多，变得腐败，倾听那些不他妈的的领导者。这就是生活的含义。像她这样的。然而，我们过着如此不幸的生活。试图购买太多尝试赚到太多的东西。当我们只需要一点时。把事情简单化。我们做了什么。
